Bianca Allen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bianca_Allen 0 Bianca Allen is a native English-speaking voice actress residing in Japan who primarily does narration voice-over work as well as characters in numerous video games. She is mostly known for her role as Carrie Fernandez from Castlevania 64, Alicia S. Tiller and Misato Hayakawa from Countdown Vampires, Tomoe Hirasaka in Fatal Frame, Reiko Hinomoto and Rowdy Reiko from Rumble Roses.
